```python
import pandas as pd

df_log = pd.DataFrame({
    "batch": ["B1","B1","B1","B2","B2","B2","B3","B3","B3","B4","B4","B4"],
    "hour":  [0, 1, 2, 0, 1, 2, 0, 1, 2, 0, 1, 2],
    "sensor": ["T","T","T","T","T","T","T","T","T","T","T","T"],
    "value":  [37.0, 37.5, 37.0, 37.0, 36.5, 36.0, 36.5, 36.5, 36.5, 37.2, 37.2, 37.2],
})
df_batch = pd.DataFrame({
    "batch": ["B1","B2","B3","B4"],
    "cell_line": ["CHO-A","CHO-A","CHO-B","CHO-B"],
    "target_temp": [37.0, 37.0, 36.5, 37.0],
    "spec_low": [36.5, 36.5, 36.0, 36.5],
    "spec_high": [37.5, 37.5, 37.0, 37.5],
})
display(df_log, df_batch)
```

```python
df_feat = df_merged.groupby('batch').agg(
    temp_mean = ('value', 'mean'),
    temp_min = ('value','min'),
    temp_max = ('value', 'max')
).reset_index()
display(df_feat)
```
